Referenced source
-----------------
The modifier set (membership, tiers, conditional exceptions) in
`src/modifiers/bliss-modifiers.js` originates from the BCI-AV head-glyph exclusions
defined by the bliss-svg-builder project
(https://github.com/hlridge/bliss-svg-builder, MPL-2.0). That source file is
referenced, not vendored; the curated glosses and explanations are this kit's own.

